movies.title: Le Mans
movies.plot: Filmed during the annual 24-hour endurance race at Le Mans, Michael Delaney is a Porsche driver haunted by the memory of an accident at the previous year's race in which a competing driver was killed. Delaney also finds himself increasingly infatuated with the man's widow.

movies.title: Nicholas and Alexandra
movies.plot: Tsar Nicholas II, the inept last monarch of Russia, insensitive to the needs of his people, is overthrown and exiled to Siberia with his family.

events.title: Tsar Nicholas II and his family are killed by Bolsheviks

movies.title: Willy Wonka & the Chocolate Factory
movies.plot: Eccentric candy man Willy Wonka prompts a worldwide frenzy when he announces that golden tickets hidden inside five of his delicious candy bars will admit their lucky holders into his top-secret confectionary. But does Wonka have an agenda hidden amid a world of Oompa Loompas and chocolate rivers?
movies.awards: Nominated for 1 Oscar. Another 2 wins & 2 nominations.

movies.title: 10 Rillington Place
movies.plot: The story of British serial killer John Christie, who committed most or all of his crimes in the titular terraced house, and the miscarriage of justice involving Timothy Evans.
